These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, gardening, baking, dancing
4 different pets are kept: snake, rabbit, guinea-pig, hedgehog
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, indonesian, polish
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, tram, trike
1. the colombian is the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the indonesian is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
3. the colombian is the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the owner of the snake is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the person driving the tram is the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
8. the canadian is on the far right##1
9. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Hobby   | gardening | dancing   | chess  | baking  |
| Pet   | rabbit    | hedgehog    | snake      | guinea-pig    |
| Nationality   | polish | colombian | indonesian | canadian |
| Transport     | trike  | bus       | jet-ski    | tram     |

