.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, house, salsa, jazz
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, lizard
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, white, black, lavender
1. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the person who likes white##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the fan of jazz is between the owner of the frog and the person who likes chestnut##2
6. the person who likes lavender is between the fan of jazz and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
8. the fan of house is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the fan of salsa is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | drawing    | singing  | cooking    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic      | house  | jazz  | salsa |
| Pet           | lizard      | frog       | dog      | bird       |
| Color         | white    | lavender | black | chestnut |

