.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
House: tower, colonial, victorian, palace
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, photography, traveling
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, lawyer, paramedic, pilot
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, superhero, time-travel, action
1. the paramedic is the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the pilot##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the victorian house is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the lawyer is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the palace house is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the tower house is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
9. the person who's hobby is photography is between the victorian house and the lawyer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| House        | colonial | victorian     | tower   | palace     |
| Hobby       | fishing   | camping   | photography | traveling |
| Job         | analyst   | paramedic | pilot       | lawyer    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel    | superhero | musical  | action    |

