4 different games are played: poker, backgammon, mah-jongg, chess
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, soccer, volleyball
 1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is the person who growsdaisy##1
 3. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the person playing backgammon##1
 6. the person playing chess is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person watching disaster movies is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
10. the person who growsazalea is between the person playing poker and the person who growsdahlia##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Flower           | daisy  | dahlia | azalea     | daffodil |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action  | martial-arts | disaster       |
| Game           | backgammon       | chess    | mah-jongg      | poker           |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | rugby   | volleyball   | soccer         |

