 7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person watching adventure movies##2
10. the person watching romance movies is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
