The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, cycling, sailing
1. the fan of folk is between the person who's sport is sailing and the fan of jazz##2
2. the person playing backgammon is between the fan of folk and the person who's birthday is in november##2
3. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's birthday is in may##2
4. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
8. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
9. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Game           | go | backgammon | monopoly  | domino |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | punk       | folk     | jazz      |
| Birthday   | november   | may      | january   | april   |
