.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, lemonade, hot-chocolate, iced-tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, designer, fisherman, social-worker
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, cooking, magic-tricks, dancing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, handball, parkour, volleyball
 1. the person drinking lemonade is the fisherman##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 3. the fisherman is the person who's sport is handball##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person drinking mirinda##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
 7. the designer is on the left of the fisherman##1
 8. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
 9. the accountant is between the social-worker and the person who's sport is cycling##2
10. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage          | iced-tea        | hot-chocolate    | mirinda | lemonade   |
| Job           | social-worker | accountant | designer   | fisherman |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks         | filmmaking       | dancing      | cooking     |
