.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, mirinda, sprite
There 4 different types of food: corn, nectarine, onion, plum
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, green, azure, yellow
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, car, bus, bike
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 2. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 3. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
 4. the person eating corn is the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 7. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the person driving the bike is between the person eating corn and the person eating onion##2
 9. the person eating plum is on the right of the person driving the car##1
10. the person who likes emerald is between the person eating corn and the person eating onion##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | mirinda    | sprite      | hot-chocolate |
| Food       | corn        | plum       | onion       | nectarine     |
| Color      | azure | emerald | yellow | green        |
| Transport        | car       | bike     | bus         | motorbike           |

